monster boy and the cursed kingdom please dont bemoan the lack of pixel art monster boy is a throwback to early 90s gaming in the best way possible this beautiful game captures the retro experience in a more meaningful way than any of the countless 2d metroidvanias ive played over the past decade its moment to moment gameplay is consistently engaging and the game maintains a steady even difficulty resulting in a game thats still surprising 15 hours in i am fawning over this game
